From: Tomi Valkeinen <tomi.valkeinen@ti.com>
Date: Wed, 16 Apr 2014 13:16:27 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 0555/1587] ARM: OMAP: add detection of omap5-dss

commit 9a3089481a2ed87517f71e00e8fc0182c604f255 upstream

Add detection of omap5-dss nodes so that the related devices get
initialized.

Signed-off-by: Tomi Valkeinen <tomi.valkeinen@ti.com>
---
 arch/arm/mach-omap2/display.c |    4 ++++
 1 files changed, 4 insertions(+), 0 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/arm/mach-omap2/display.c b/arch/arm/mach-omap2/display.c
index 4a56ad3..2f840f9 100644
--- a/arch/arm/mach-omap2/display.c
+++ b/arch/arm/mach-omap2/display.c
@@ -570,6 +570,10 @@ struct device_node * __init omapdss_find_dss_of_node(void)
 	if (node)
 		return node;
 
+	node = of_find_compatible_node(NULL, NULL, "ti,omap5-dss");
+	if (node)
+		return node;
+
 	return NULL;
 }
 
